_sText: Attention: new Version 1.4 Map made by ~dude~ Skybox by Solidsurf Machinegun-model by GSC/OLAF version: 1.3 - more camping and waiting spots ---> longer play-time - two ways to get inside the balloon - a passage throw the spawn position ---> player can choose the way to escape - fixed canal problem version: 1.4 - no block-damage on the door of the white house - no stuck on the house in the near of the second escape way I hope you enjoy the map
